  "title": "Draughtsman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare AutoCAD drawings</li>\n  <li>Prepare submissions of AutoCAD drawings from conceptual design up to construction development</li>\n  <li>Produce 2D and 3D drawings using AutoCAD application according to customer’s specification</li>\n  <li>Assist Project Engineer on site measurement</li>\n  <li>Ensure that all drawings are done in accordance with company’s quality procedure</li>\n  <li>Liaise with clients to ensure specifications have been met</li>\n  <li>Assist in modification of reports and specifications</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering or any relevant engineering discipline</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years’ experience in M&amp;E and interior design multi-layer architectural drawing</li>\n  <li><strong>Proficient in AutoCAD, 3DMax and BIM modelling</strong></li>\n  <li>Professional certificate in BIM modelling</li>\n  <li>Ability to achieve drawing with high degree of accuracy</li>\n</ul>",
